<br>
Why do some of the greatest advocates of role playing on this server have to be such prima donnas. A few people-skills and they would be at the forefront of rp'ing on Firiona Vie. Instead, they always seem to want to light the toilet paper on fire.<br>
<br>
Bane, whatever floats your boat. I wish you well but like Senshi, you long for a server that will never exist. Doesn't jousting with windmills ever get old?<br>
<br>
Too bad there aren't private EQ servers like there are with UO emulators. Given their own server, I think Bane and Senshi would create a world that would be enormously engrossing and fun. But it will never, ever happen on a public EQ server. Legends sure as hell won't be it. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uroninsenshi.showPublicProfile?language=EN>RoninSenshi</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://members.aol.com/sageofthehalo/Kanji.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Senshi No Adakia</span><br>  Posts: 365<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(2/2/02 11:45:06 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1258.topic&index=31>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/sageofthehalo/Kanji.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: RP advocates</span><hr size=1> I'm sorry I never had a life.<br>
